🍉️1. We can comment two ways one is using -- and another is /* shown below
  --> --select name from company;

      /* I have writen
       something in these
      three lines */


🍉️2. Expressions : as,
  --> select name as employe_name from company; 	(Note : as)

  --> select count(*) from company;			(note : count(*) -- to count all number of row)

  --> select max(age) from company;			(Note : max(age) -- to know max value of the particular column)

  --> select sum(salary) from company;			(Note : sum)

  --> select avg(salary) from company;			(Note : avg)

  --> select current_timestamp;				(Note : current_timestamp)
 
  --> select current_timestamp from company where age=26; (Note : custom timestamp)
